Detailed Description

Represents a partition of the APOXI MimeTypeTable.

Currently only two partitions are allowed ! One of them is directly instantiated by MimeTypeTable and contains the MIME types directly defined by APOXI. A second instance may be allocated by user SW to support additional MIME types which are normally not supported by APOXI. User SW should not explicitly instantiate Partition. Instead, include file MimeTypeTableUtils.hpp and use the helper macros found there.
